data.description: This lovely 3-bedroom 2 bath home in Clovis, is located in the Clovis Unified School District and is conveniently located near restaurants, stores and more! This home is just waiting for the perfect buyer! As you walk in the front door into the entryway, you can feel how airy and light the home feels. to your right you enter the kitchen complete with a breakfast nook, pantry and bar. The open concept family room features a lovely fireplace to keep you cozy on those cold winter nights. The master bedroom is large and airy, with an updated master bathroom. Down the hall you have 2 more bedrooms and the guest bathroom which has new lvp flooring. To top all of this off the home features a lovely sparkling POOL for the hot summer days! So what are you waiting for? Make your appointment today!
